'''白南準'''（{{lang-ko|백남준}}，Nam June Paik；{{bd|1932年|7月20日|2006年|1月29日}}），[[韩裔美国人|韩裔美国]]艺术家。他运用多种不同媒介，并被认为是[[影像艺术|影像艺术]]的开创者。<ref>Noah Wardrip-Fruin and Nick Montfort, ''The New Media Reader'', MIT Press, 2003, p227. {{ISBN|0-262-23227-8}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/going-out-guide/post/father-of-video-art-nam-june-paik-gets-american-art-museum-exhibit-photos/2012/12/12/c16fa980-448b-11e2-8e70-e1993528222d_blog.html | work=The Washington Post | first=Maura | last=Judkis | title="Father of video art" Nam June Paik gets American Art Museum exhibit (Photos) | date=December 12, 2012 | accessdate=2021-02-14 | archive-date=2017-08-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809041026/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/going-out-guide/post/father-of-video-art-nam-june-paik-gets-american-art-museum-exhibit-photos/2012/12/12/c16fa980-448b-11e2-8e70-e1993528222d_blog.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 他也被认为是第一个用“电子高速公路”（"electronic super highway"）一词来描述[[电子通信|电子通信]]的未来的人。<ref>{{cite news
